This paper is about large scale video classification using machine learning techniques. The paper discusses the use of multiple models, feature space augmentation, regularization, and ensembling to improve the performance of the classification system. Given this, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is computer vision (cs.CV), followed by machine learning (cs.LG), multimedia (cs.MM), information retrieval (cs.IR), and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
